Package project_4

Class MenuItem

java.lang.Object
project_4.MenuItem
Direct Known Subclasses:
Coffee, Donut
public class MenuItem
extends java.lang.Object
This is the superclass of all menu items, such as donuts and coffee. Any class defined for a menu item must extend this class. All the subclasses must include a “itemPrice” method for calculating the price of the menu item. -2 points for each violation.
Author:
KJ Wang, Mehdi Kamal
